skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: mind guru
des:
Mind Guru is a skill that tells you relaxing phrases to help you find positive thoughts and brighten your day. Our minds are powerful and have a great influence in the way we see and feel the world around us. Mind Guru helps you boost your mood.
To use this skill, enable it. The you can ask the following:

'Alexa, ask Mind guru a relaxing quote'
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
